  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Needs Review\n83\n-15-\n\nactual reality (the informational basis) or even to other realities. Alternate realities (i.e. programs). Our flux (what I called \"mundane\") world is the print-out from the \"sacred\" which is the narrative oasis, the verbal/written/informational program itself (like the Torah); ah; the Torah is trie basis of Israel's reality. As Acts is for Christians. I've been flimflammed...for example by VALIS theological overkill (mentioning too many saviors). It can run many programs si",
      "matched_alias": "Israel",
